OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy to start with, the cloud soon
OL,7,Fthickening from the west to bring a
OL,8,Ffew outbreaks of mostly light rain
OL,9,Fthrough the early hours. The rain may
OL,10,Fbe a little heavier across the
OL,11,FCheviots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FGenerally cloudy with a few
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain in the morning,
OL,15,Ffollowed by slow-moving showers that
OL,16,Fmay become locally heavy later in the
OL,17,Fafternoon. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
