OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FFairly
OL,6,Fcloudy with showers on Wednesday, some
OL,7,Fbrief sunny spells. A wet and windy
OL,8,Fstart on Thursday, drier and brighter
OL,9,Flater. Dry with sunny spells on
OL,10,FFriday, though breezy.
